    <item>
      <title>加拿大释放公共土地解决住房短缺问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/canada-frees-up-public-lands-to-tackle-housing-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府确定了 56 处联邦地产，面积相当于约 2,000 个冰球场，可在这些地产上建造数百套新的经济适用房，以应对可用土地稀缺导致的住房短缺问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/canada-frees-up-public-lands-to-tackle-housing-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 17:04:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列轰炸黎巴嫩阻止袭击 中东局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/mideast-on-edge-after-israel-bombs-lebanon-to-thwart-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在一百架以色列战机飞越黎巴嫩南部、摧毁真主党数千个导弹发射器（所谓先发制人打击）几个小时后，中东地区仍然做好了应对可能涉及伊朗及其盟友民兵的扩大战火的准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/mideast-on-edge-after-israel-bombs-lebanon-to-thwart-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 16:18:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
